  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "The fourth Nintendo DS entry in the Beyblade: Metal Masters series.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "It starts with which ever character use choose in the game. (They all have the same story)\n\nPlayer gets a strange letter from Agito, which is an invite to compete in the \"Beyblade World Championships\" at Dyna Cemetery to determine the best blader.\n\nThe character fights a few battles and then fights regular Agito and Dino Agito, when he's defeated he is lifted from the possesion of Nightmare Rex.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    }
  ]
